\@writefile{toc}{\contentsline {section}{\numberline {6}Interpretation {\small  \textcolor {tfgold}{\textbf  {[P]}}}: the self-reproducing cosmic cycle}{6}{section.6}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{sec:cycle}{{6}{6}{Interpretation \tP : the self-reproducing cosmic cycle}{section.6}{}}
\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {5}{\ignorespaces {\small  \textcolor {tfgold}{\textbf  {[P]}}}\ The cyclic reading. Each cycle: $U_k$ collapses; unitarity keeps the information on the horizon (the seam, carrying $c_3=\tfrac  1{8\pi }$); the gapped boundary transport contracts it to the rank-$1$ attractor (the ``law'', \S  \ref {sec:attractor}); that seeds $U_{k+1}$. The $\mathbb  Z_2=g_{\mathrm  {car}}-N_{\mathrm  {fam}}$ sheet parity is the M\"obius/two-sided (thermofield-double) gluing across the horizon. Realized constants $=$ the attractor's fixed point, hence parameter-free.}}{7}{figure.5}\protected@file@percent }
